edu.umass.cs.gnscommon

Class GNSCommandProtocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnscommon.GNSCommandProtocol

  • public class GNSCommandProtocol
extends Object
    This class defines a GNSCommandProtocol. Which is to say that it defines a bunch of constants that define the protocol support for communicating between the client and the local name server. See also CommandType.
    Version:
    1.18
    Author:
    arun, Westy
